## Job Description
Mifu is a startup founded by two recent graduates from the University of Bristol that focuses on micro-influencer marketing at scale.
Mifu is looking for a freelance frontend developer to update and develop new features, working with the CTO and and Cloud Engineer.

www.mifu.co.uk
## Job Responsibilities
You will be working in NextJS (React) to display and manipluate data from the API to be shown on the frontend. 
You will be expected to take features/bugs/updates from a Trello style board and implement them. 
Git will be extensively used.

